备份存储</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/function_principle/onpremise/storage/backupstorage/</link><description>Recent content in 备份存储 on Cloudpods</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><lastBuildDate>Tue, 15 Mar 2022 15:55:34 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/function_principle/onpremise/storage/backupstorage/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Docs: 新建备份存储</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/function_principle/onpremise/storage/backupstorage/create/</link><pubDate>Tue, 15 Mar 2022 16:24:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/function_principle/onpremise/storage/backupstorage/create/</guid><description>
&lt;p>目前仅支持添加NFS共享存储作为备份存储。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="前置条件">前置条件&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>要求所有宿主机都能通过网络访问备份存储，可以在任意宿主机节点尝试挂载备份存储&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="创建方式">创建方式&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>可以通过前端WebUI创建，也可以通过如下climc命令创建。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="color:#8f5902;font-style:italic"># 添加备份存储，目前--capacity-mb字段无意义，可随便填写&lt;/span>
$ climc backupstorage-create &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>--storage-type &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">{&lt;/span>nfs&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">}]&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>--nfs-host NFS_HOST&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">]&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>--nfs-shared-dir NFS_SHARED_DIR&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">]&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>--capacity-mb CAPACITY_MB&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">]&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">[&lt;/span>--description &amp;lt;DESCRIPTION&amp;gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold">]&lt;/span> &amp;lt;NAME&amp;gt;
&lt;span style="color:#8f5902;font-style:italic"># 举例，将存储地址`192.168.1.1`，文件路径`/data/nfs`的nfs存储添加到备份存储&lt;/span>
$ climc backupstorage-create --storage-type nfs --nfs-host 192.168.1.1 --nfs-shared-dir /data/nfs --capacity-mb &lt;span style="color:#0000cf;font-weight:bold">100000&lt;/span> backupstorage
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>